### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### Get Statistics
GET http://localhost:8080/stats

### Get all keys
GET http://localhost:8080/kv/

### Get keys with prefix filter
GET http://localhost:8080/kv/?prefix=user

### Get keys with limit
GET http://localhost:8080/kv/?limit=5

### Get keys with prefix and limit
GET http://localhost:8080/kv/?prefix=session&limit=10

### Create a new key
POST http://localhost:8080/kv/username
Content-Type: text/plain

John Doe

### Create another key
POST http://localhost:8080/kv/user:123
Content-Type: text/plain

{"id": 123, "name": "Alice"}

### Create with prefix
POST http://localhost:8080/kv/session:abc123
Content-Type: text/plain

active

### Get a specific key
GET http://localhost:8080/kv/username

### Get key information
GET http://localhost:8080/kv/username/info

### Check if key exists
GET http://localhost:8080/kv/username/exists

### Check if non-existent key exists
GET http://localhost:8080/kv/nonexistent/exists

### Update an existing key
PUT http://localhost:8080/kv/username
Content-Type: text/plain

Jane Doe

### Try to create existing key (should fail with 409)
POST http://localhost:8080/kv/username
Content-Type: text/plain

Another Name

### Try to update non-existent key (should fail)
PUT http://localhost:8080/kv/nonexistent
Content-Type: text/plain

Some Value

### Search by regex
GET http://localhost:8080/kv/r/^user

### Search by regex - specific pattern
GET http://localhost:8080/kv/r/^user:[0-9]+$

